|3 |  └─SORT                 |     |1       |6           |
|4 |    └─SUBPLAN SCAN       |VIEW1|1       |6           |
|5 |      └─MERGE JOIN       |     |1       |6           |
|6 |        ├─TABLE FULL SCAN|a    |1       |3           |
|7 |        └─TABLE FULL SCAN|b    |5       |3           |
==========================================================
